Description: Enabling authenticating of users from different identity providers in shiny
    using oAuth / OpenIDC protocol. Supporting Auth0 and Keycloac (More to come).
    Federation to other identity providers like Azure, Google, Facebook and others is possible through Auth0 and Keycloak.
    Not reliant on Shiny Server Pro.
